column5:
4 pages, 2 figures, 6th Meeting on Hot Subdwarf Stars and Related
  Objects, eds. Van Grootel, V.; Green, E.; Fontaine, G.; Charpinet, S.;
  Astronomical Society of the Pacific Conference Series Vol. 481, p.307

column11:
  The aim of this note is to point out some inaccuracies in our paper \cite{HD}
and to fix them. Some new notions are introduced and properties of them are
investigated.
